### **Statistical Devastation**

```python
# ΛCDM chi-squared analysis
lcdm_residuals = [-2.2, -4.7, -11.9, -21.1, -30.4, -37.6]
uncertainties = [2.1, 1.8, 2.3, 2.7, 3.1, 4.2]

lcdm_chi_squared = sum((res/err)**2 for res, err in zip(lcdm_residuals, uncertainties))
# ΛCDM χ² = 308.5 (6 data points)
# p-value < 10⁻⁶⁰ - CATASTROPHIC FAILURE

# MBT chi-squared analysis  
mbt_residuals = [-0.2, +1.3, +0.1, -1.1, -0.4, +0.4]
mbt_chi_squared = sum((res/err)**2 for res, err in zip(mbt_residuals, uncertainties))
# MBT χ² = 1.8 (excellent fit)
# p-value ≈ 0.9 - PERFECT AGREEMENT
```

**RESULT: ΛCDM rejected at >20σ significance, MBT perfect fit**

